But bleſſed be Almighty God, who hath long ſince miraculouſly confuted their abominable Principles, and Practices, and vindicated the Honour of his own Reverend Name;
Pſal. 111.9. who hath ſignally approved the pious bounty of ſuch as loved our Nation,

